highlights.text: “Boy's a liar Pt. 2” by PinkPantheress and Ice Spice is the highest new entry on Top Songs Imphal at #73.
“Malang Sajna” by Sachet Tandon, Parampara Tandon, and Kumaar is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Imphal, up 44 spots at #50.
The Weeknd has the most spots on Top Songs Imphal. “Reminder” is the highest at #1.
“Maan Meri Jaan” by King has been on Top Songs Imphal the longest, at 13 weeks straight.
